.row.center.middle
	.panel.panel-signin.column-6--hand

		h1 Login
		p.small
			| Accounts are reset on server restart from 
			code dummydata.coffee
			| . Default account is 
			code test@test.com 
			| / 
			code test

		form(name="form", ng-submit="login(form)", novalidate="novalidate")

			.form-group
				label Email
				input(type="text", name="email", ng-model="user.email")

			.form-group
				label Password
				input(type="password", name="password", ng-model="user.password")

			.form-group.has-error
				p(ng-show="form.email.$error.required && form.password.$error.required && submitted")
					| Please enter your email and password.
				p {{ errors.other }}

			button.button.button-large(type="submit") Sign in

		hr
		small
			| Not registered? 
			a(href="/signup") Create an account.